A tiny database that stores structured data + unstructured embeddings + can be queried in natural language.

### **Core features**

- Custom file-based storage engine (SQLite hybrid)
- Embedding index using cosine-sim search
- Natural-language â†’ structured query translation using a small local LLM
- Web dashboard using FastAPI + WebSockets for live indexing view
- Plugins to sync data with local folders
